quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  11,89,"Waya qawmi la yajrimannakumshiqaqee an yuseebakum mithlu ma asabaqawma noohin aw qawma hoodin aw qawma salihinwama qawmu lootin minkum bibaAAeed"
  11,90,"Wastaghfiroo rabbakum thumma toobooilayhi inna rabbee raheemun wadood"
  11,91,"Qaloo ya shuAAaybu manafqahu katheeran mimma taqoolu wa-inna lanarakafeena daAAeefan walawla rahtukalarajamnaka wama anta AAalayna biAAazeez"
  11,92,"Qala ya qawmi arahteeaAAazzu AAalaykum mina Allahi wattakhathtumoohuwaraakum thihriyyan inna rabbee bimataAAmaloona muheet"
  11,93,"Waya qawmi iAAmaloo AAala makanatikuminnee AAamilun sawfa taAAlamoona man ya/teehi AAathabunyukhzeehi waman huwa kathibun wartaqiboo innemaAAakum raqeeb"
  11,94,"Walamma jaa amrunanajjayna shuAAayban wallatheena amanoomaAAahu birahmatin minna waakhathati allatheenathalamoo assayhatu faasbahoofee diyarihim jathimeen"
  11,95,"Kaan lam yaghnaw feeha alabuAAdan limadyana kama baAAidat thamood"
  11,96,"Walaqad arsalna moosa bi-ayatinawasultanin mubeen"
  11,97,"Ila firAAawna wamala-ihi fattabaAAooamra firAAawna wama amru firAAawna birasheed"
